<p><a name="Anti-death_penalty" id="Anti-death_penalty"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Capital_punishment_in_the_United_States&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Edit section: Anti-death penalty">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Anti-death penalty</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://ncadp.org" class="external text" title="http://ncadp.org" rel="nofollow">National Coalition to Abolish the Death Penalty</a></li>
